{{Quote|Its ancestral sword, Ice, was forged in ancient Valyria and has been passed down through the generations.|[[Bran Stark]]|Complete Guide to Westeros}}
'''Ice''' was a [[Valyrian steel]] greatsword and an heirloom of [[House Stark]]. It was used both in war and on ceremonial occasions by the Lord of [[Winterfell]].
